      </mj-column>
    </mj-section>
    <mj-section background-color="white" padding="20px 30px">
      <mj-column>
        <mj-spacer />
        <mj-text><multiline>Hi James,</multiline></mj-text>
        <mj-spacer />
        <mj-text><multiline>I have listed your account details below for your reference.</multiline></mj-text>
      </mj-column>
    </mj-section>
    <mj-section background-color="white" padding="20px 30px" >
      <mj-column>
        <mj-divider border-width="1px" border-style="solid" border-color="#ddd" padding="0 0 30px 0" />
        <mj-text>
          <ul class="list-data">
            <li><strong>Our Reference:</strong> <span>6435 1020</span></li>
            <li><strong>Account Type:</strong> <span>Panthera Test Client</span></li>
            <li><strong>Client Reference:</strong> <span>TEST001</span></li>
            <li><strong>Amount Paid:</strong> <span>$2,153.34</span></li>
            <li><strong>Amount Outstanding:</strong> <span>$1,037.21</span></li>
          </ul>
        </mj-text>
        <mj-divider border-width="1px" border-style="solid" border-color="#ddd" padding="15px 0 0" /> 
        <mj-spacer height="30px" />
        <mj-text>
          <multiline>Please note, we are committed to respecting the financial, health and social well-being of all our customers, and we are here to provide support and flexibility throughout this difficult time.</multiline>
        </mj-text>
        <mj-spacer />
        <mj-text>
          <multiline>If there is anything you wish to discuss, please don't hesitate to contact our office on <a href="tel:1300 722 974">1300 722 974</a> to speak with one of our friendly staff.</multiline>
        </mj-text>
        <mj-spacer />
        <mj-text>
          <multiline>Alternatively, please advise your intentions towards the above account so we can assist moving forward?</multiline>
        </mj-text>
        <mj-spacer />
        <mj-text>
          <multiline>You can also manage your account online via our customer portal at <a href="https://www.pantherafinance.com.au" targe="_blank">www.pantherafinance.com.au</a>.</multiline>
        </mj-text>
        <mj-spacer />
        <mj-text><multiline>Yours faithfully,</multiline></mj-text>
        <mj-spacer />
        <mj-text>
          <multiline>Dawn Donnelly <br />
          General Manager</multiline>
        </mj-text>
        <mj-spacer height="30px" />
        <mj-button mj-class="fullwidth-button" background-color="#009d8b">Make a payment</mj-button>
        <mj-button mj-class="fullwidth-button" background-color="#009d8b">View Payment Plans</mj-button>
        <mj-button mj-class="fullwidth-button" background-color="#e5872c">Why are you hearing from us?</mj-button>
        <mj-spacer height="30px" />
      </mj-column>
    </mj-section>
    <mj-section background-url="https://tomdevvn90.github.io/panthera-mail-template/images/contact-us-background.png" background-color="black" padding="40px 30px 30px">
      <mj-column>
        <mj-text font-size="22px" font-weight="bold" color="white">
          <multiline>Other ways to contact us</multiline>
        </mj-text>
        <mj-spacer />
        <mj-text>
